<!--
 FurBot Realese Version Shield With Official Logotype Provided By Icons8
-->

> <img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/FurBot-1.0r1-red?style=flat-square&logo=data:image/png;base64,"/>
>
> * **FurBot** is a bot written for the
>  `VKontakte`  social network in
>  order to pump out pictures
>  from the `e926.net` website.

<!--
 Python Version And Python Coverage Shield With Official Logotype
-->
> <img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/python-3.7-red?style=flat-square&logo=python&logoColor=white"/> <img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/coverage-97%25-red?style=flat-square&logo=python&logoColor=white"/>
> 
> * **FurBot** is fully written in Python
> and requires It of version 3.7 or Above.

<!--
 Vkontakte Shield With Official Logotype
-->
> <img src="https://img.shields.io/github/pipenv/locked/dependency-version/FluffyMak4ic/Fur.Bot/vk-api/FoxsomeRework?color=red&style=flat-square&logo=vk&logoColor=white"/>
> 
> * **FurBot** uses Python Vkontakte API
>  to handle messages  from users. More
>  about commands you can find in the
>  Furbot Documentation.

<!--
 AIOHTTP Shield With Non-Official Logotype
-->
> <img src="https://img.shields.io/github/pipenv/locked/dependency-version/FluffyMak4ic/Fur.Bot/aiohttp?color=red&style=flat-square&logo=data:image/png;base64,"/>
>
> * **FurBot** uses *AIOHttp* to download
>  images from the Web asynchronously.
